SystemRequirements:
    MeCab 0.996 or higher for Japanese and Chinese (libmecab-dev (deb),
    mecab-devel (rpm)), mecab-jieba 0.1.1 for Mandarin Chinese
    (https://github.com/lindera/mecab-jieba), mecab-ko 0.999
    (https://github.com/Pusnow/mecab-ko-msvc) for Korean
